description: More than 350 people, including 150 rescued by Banksy's boat, have left a Mediterranean rescue ship.
title: Louise Michel: Migrants rescued by Banksy boat to disembark in Sicily
title_page: Louise Michel: Migrants rescued by Banksy boat to disembark in Sicily - BBC News
maintext: While the number is far lower than at the peak of Europe's migrant crisis in 2015, the crossing remains dangerous: an estimated 554 migrants have died so far this year, according to the International Organization for Migration (IOM).
